ove.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e760882582096ef14063e128b5091158d602adb","tid":114106,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T01:34:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>俾貴錢買廢水<br />\n香港又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買完仲要倒落海 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不嬲係話要香港買廢水做treatment 放海<br />\n<br />\n出埋豉油出埋雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92254ddff861620a830902536dc95ee6e6356f3c","tid":114106,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天價買臭水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再倒落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}